ğŸš€ 6. The â€œDonâ€™t Panicâ€ Rule
You donâ€™t need to master all of UVM right away. Just remember the pattern and build small working examples first:

âœ… Minimal pieces to start:
Sequence item
Sequence
Sequencer
Driver
Monitor
Agent
Env
Test

Focus on data flow (sequence â†’ DUT â†’ monitor) and youâ€™ll be fine.
Youâ€™ll add layers (scoreboard, coverage, factory overrides) later.

