ğŸ§© 7. Quick Recap
Concept	                              Role	                                         Analogy
Sequence Item	                   Data structure                             	Packet / transaction
Sequence	                       Traffic generator	                               Produces packets
Sequencer                        	Middleman	                                           Dispatcher
